1.  Flexbox is modern layout mode in css3
2.  Flex is a value for the display property
3.  Replaces float and is much more elegant to work with
4.  Align item both horizontal(row) and vertical(column)
5.  Flex items can be re-ordered via CSS

Setting display: flex will automatically align all the child divs horizontally

Align properties

justify-content: ALign along the main axis(horizontal)
align-items: Align items along the cross axis(vertical)
align-content: Align when extra space in cross axis
